channel.title: How do I Put My InsidiaX Server Online?
channel.description: i downloaded insidiax and coded it a little bit but i have no idea how to put it online, i cant change the server ip and when i change the client ip i cant connect...idk what to do! someone please help!

item.title: How do I Put My InsidiaX Server Online?
item.dc:creator: @ultimatepkvillage ultimatepkvillage
item.description:
@ultimatepkvillage wrote:

your probably connecting to your no-ip which only allows other people to connect or having utorrent up could also be a problem try using 127.0.0.1 and to make it online you need to portforward through your router portforward.com find your router model then follow the guide to runescape private server if they dont have your router model find something close to it if none exist google.com
